Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Freedom of Information Act
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bx32
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 25 Feb 1979
Freedom of Information Act reveals government is collecting computer data on US citizens. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less